data.description: This well-maintained ranch/rambler is located only minutes from I-66. This mountain paradise, nestled on 1.19 acre, is the perfect mountain home retreat. The home boasts two bedrooms and two full bathrooms on the main level and a large family room and bonus room in the basement. Other amenities include, a spacious main level deck off the kitchen and front porch, a screened in porch on the lower level off the laundry room, and a large shed. Plus, the home is partially fenced in the back! It also has a flat, well maintained circular driveway, a large, cleared flat side yard, as well as plenty of parking adjacent to the home next to the outdoor storage shed. The poles in the basement (as shown in the photos) have been converted into columns since photos were taken for a much nicer finished look. Radon remediation already in place. The corner gas fireplace in living room can easily be removed if desired--it is not currently hooked up to any gas tanks. SimpliSafe video doorbell conveys. There are also a few SimpliSafe room and door sensors, and they too will convey. Plus there is a Nest Thermostat! Welcome home!!
